reviews.review_text: Eyes Intro to Eyes.... I was fortunate to catch all 6 of these Garden shows.  I loved most nights for they all had a moment (this was not always true in the 12 garden run nights. This year was special... on this night Jerry would not step forward completely to mic. He would approach stop and keep JAMMING!  Nothing was out of the question it seemed after the 10.14 Scarlet>Fire that was very long and just fantastic...Jerry kept into surfing eyes for many minutes, Jerry has always approached the mic to sing almost immediately during EYES.   I mention this to a few friends in the moment they are overtaken by the beauty and hadn't noticed.
